{% extends "layout.jinja" %}

{% block title %}Privacy Policy - RAI{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
<style>
p {
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    padding-left: 0.8em;
}
ul.ul {
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5em;
}
a.clink {
    text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>
{% endblock head %}

{% block contents %}
<section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col gap-y-2 items-center justify-center bg-primary-950 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-white">
    <div class="bg-primary-900 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-xl"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 12/12/2025</p>
        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">1. Introduction</h3>
            <p>This Privacy Policy explains how RAI (“we”, “our”, “us”) collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our platform to create or chat with AI models.</p>
            <p>By using RAI, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">2. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>We collect only the information necessary to create and maintain your account and operate the service.</p>
            <p>This includes:</p>
            <ul class="ul">
                <li>Username</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Password (securely hashed)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We may also automatically collect basic usage data such as device type, browser type, and general interaction with the platform for security and performance reasons.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
            <ul class="ul">
                <li>Create and manage user accounts</li>
                <li>Provide and improve the RAI platform</li>
                <li>Maintain security and prevent abuse</li>
                <li>Respond to support requests</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Your personal data is not sold to any third parties.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">4. AI Interactions & User Content</h3>
            <p>When you create AI models or chat with them, your inputs may be stored so the platform can function properly. You retain ownership of your content.</p>
            <p>Your content may be used to:</p>
            <ul class="ul">
                <li>Operate the AI features</li>
                <li>Improve service performance</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not publicly share your private chats or model data unless you choose to publish them.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">5. Cookies & Tracking</h3>
            <p>RAI may use basic cookies or similar technologies to maintain login sessions and improve performance. We do not use invasive tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">6. Data Security</h3>
            <p>We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including:</p>
            <ul class="ul">
                <li>Hashed and salted passwords</li>
                <li>Secure servers</li>
                <li>Access controls</li>
            </ul>
            <p>No system is 100% secure, but we work to protect your information from unauthorized access.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">7. Children’s Privacy</h3>
            <p>RAI is not intended for children under 13 (or the minimum age in your region). We do not knowingly collect data from minors below this requirement.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">8. International Use</h3>
            <p>Your information may be processed in India or other regions where our services operate. By using RAI, you consent to this global data processing.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">9. Data Retention</h3>
            <p>We retain information for as long as your account is active, or as needed to provide the service. You may request deletion of your data at any time.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">10. Your Rights</h3>
            <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="ul">
                <li>Access your personal data</li>
                <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
                <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
                <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You can contact us to exercise these rights.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">11. Third-Party Services</h3>
            <p>We do not share your personal data with external companies unless required for essential service operations or legal compliance.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">12. Changes to This Policy</h3>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy when necessary. The “Last Updated” date will change accordingly. Continued use of RAI means you accept the updated policy.</p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">13. Contact</h3>
            <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, contact us at: <a class='clink text-primary-300' href="/contact">our contact page</a></p>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}